[src:dom-events/api-event] This is the object to which the event is currently slated to be sent.
[src:dom-events/api-event] It's possible this has been changed along the way through *retargeting*.
[src:dom-events/api-event] Indicates whether or not the call to `event.preventDefault()` canceled the event.
