[src:dom-events/api-event] It is one of the following numbers: `NONE`, `CAPTURING_PHASE`, `AT_TARGET`, `BUBBLING_PHASE`.
[src:dom-events/api-event] Indicates whether or not the event was initiated by the browser (after a user click, for instance) or by a script (using an event creation method, for example).
